laralux (0.3.0-1) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Enforce single instance: opening the app while running focuses the
    existing window instead of spawning a duplicate.
  * App icon ships at standard sizes (32/128/256/512) so it resolves in
    the dock/taskbar (was a single non-standard 671x671 size).

